<p><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:13.5pt"><strong><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">简单的表格</span></strong><strong><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> &lt;table&gt;
                &lt;tr&gt;&lt;th&gt;&lt;td&gt;</span></strong></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">表格由</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> &lt;table&gt;
            </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">标签来定义。每个表格均有若干行（由</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> &lt;tr&gt;
            </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">标签定义），每行被分割为若干单元格（由</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> &lt;td&gt;
            </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">标签定义）。字母</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> td </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">指表格数据（</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">table
                data</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">），即数据单元格的内容。数据单元格可以包含文本、图片、列表、段落、表单、水平线、表格等等。</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&lt;tr&gt;
            </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">元素定义表格中的行。 同一行可同时出现</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&lt;td&gt;
            </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">和</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&lt;th&gt;
            </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">元素</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&lt;td&gt;
            </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">元素
                定义了一个包含数据的表格单元格，</span></span><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&lt;</span></span><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">td&gt;</span></span><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">有以下属性：</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<table cellspacing="0" summary=""
    style="border-collapse:collapse; border-color:#a3a3a3; border-style:solid; border-width:1px;  margin-left:32px;"
    class=" cke_show_border">

                <p><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                                style="color:white"><strong>属性</strong></span></span></span></p>
            </td>
            <td
                style="background-color:black; border-bottom:1px solid #a3a3a3; border-left:1px solid #a3a3a3; border-right:1px solid #a3a3a3; border-top:1px solid #a3a3a3; vertical-align:top; width:6.7638in">
                <p><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                                style="color:white"><strong>描述</strong></span></span></span></p>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td
                style="background-color:white; border-bottom:1px solid #a3a3a3; border-left:1px solid #a3a3a3; border-right:1px solid #a3a3a3; border-top:1px solid #a3a3a3; vertical-align:top; width:1.0548in">
                <p><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">colspan</span></span></p>
            </td>
            <td
                style="background-color:white; border-bottom:1px solid #a3a3a3; border-left:1px solid #a3a3a3; border-right:1px solid #a3a3a3; border-top:1px solid #a3a3a3; vertical-align:top; width:6.7638in">
                <p><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">此属性包含一个非负整数值，指示单元格扩展了多少列。其默认值为</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> 1</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">。</span></span></p>
                <p><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">大于</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> 1000 </span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">的值将被视为不正确，并将设置为默认值</span></span></p>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td
                style="background-color:#e7e6e6; border-bottom:1px solid #a3a3a3; border-left:1px solid #a3a3a3; border-right:1px solid #a3a3a3; border-top:1px solid #a3a3a3; vertical-align:top; width:1.0548in">
                <p><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">headers</span></span></p>
            </td>
            <td
                style="background-color:#e7e6e6; border-bottom:1px solid #a3a3a3; border-left:1px solid #a3a3a3; border-right:1px solid #a3a3a3; border-top:1px solid #a3a3a3; vertical-align:top; width:6.8333in">
                <p><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">此属性包含以空格分隔的字符串列表，每个字符串对应于应用于此元素的</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> &lt;th&gt; </span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">元素的</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> id </span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">属性。</span></span></p>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td
                style="background-color:white; border-bottom:1px solid #a3a3a3; border-left:1px solid #a3a3a3; border-right:1px solid #a3a3a3; border-top:1px solid #a3a3a3; vertical-align:top; width:1.0548in">
                <p><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">rowspan</span></span></p>
            </td>
            <td
                style="background-color:white; border-bottom:1px solid #a3a3a3; border-left:1px solid #a3a3a3; border-right:1px solid #a3a3a3; border-top:1px solid #a3a3a3; vertical-align:top; width:6.7638in">
                <p><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">此属性包含一个非负整数值，指示单元格扩展了多少行。它的默认值为</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> 1</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">；</span></span></p>
                <p><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">如果它的值设置为</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> 0</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">，它会一直延伸到单元格所属的表格部分（</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&lt;thead&gt;</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">、</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&lt;tbody&gt; (en-US)</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">、</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&lt;tfoot&gt;</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">，即使是隐式定义）的末尾。</span></span></p>
                <p><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">高于</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> 65534 </span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">的值将被缩减为</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> 65534</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">。</span></span></p>
            </td>
